#: ../../introduction/screenshots.rst:104 a0f82536b62a4b89993ab5a51902f853
msgid ""
"Qubes’ unique DisposableVMs (DispVMs) allow the user to open any file in "
"a disposable VM in a matter of seconds! A file can be edited in a "
"disposable VM, and any changes are projected back onto the original file."
" Currently, there is no way to mark files to be automatically opened in a"
" disposable VM (one needs to right-click on the file and choose the “View"
" in DisposableVM” or “Edit in DisposableVM” option), but this is planned "
"for the R2 Beta 3 release."
msgstr ""

